*&quot;Most Wanted Presents: Raja Ram the Godfather&quot; (2005)
*&quot;Evolution of Expanded Consciousness&quot; (2006)
*&quot;Raja Ram&#x27;s Stash Bag Volume 4&quot; (2006)
*&quot;The Anthology&quot; (2007)
*&quot;Raja Ram&#x27;s Pipe Dreams&quot; (2013)
