<text>Dipsosaurus is a genus of lizards in the family Iguanidae.

==Taxonomy==
Currently, there are two described species in this genus.
* Desert iguana, &quot;Dipsosaurus dorsalis&quot; 
* Catalina desert iguana, &quot;Dipsosaurus catalinensis&quot; 

