*Review by Barbara Davies (1987) in &quot;Vector&quot; 137
*Review by Faren Miller (1987) in &quot;Locus&quot;, #315 April 1987
*Review by David Langford (1987) in &quot;Foundation&quot;, #40 Summer 1987
